Package: mmetrics
Type: Package
Title: Easy Computation of Marketing Metrics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Shinichi", "Takayanagi", , "shinichi.takayanagi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Nagi", "Teramo", , "teramonagi@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
  person("Takahiro", "Yoshinaga", , "t.yoshinaga0106@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: Provides a mechanism for easy computation of marketing metrics.
  By default in this package, metrics for digital marketing (e.g. CTR, CVR, CPC etc) are calculated but you can define your own metrics easily.
  In addition to taht, you can change an analysis axis to calculate these metrics.
URL: https://github.com/shinichi-takayanagi/mmetrics
